          <p class="terminal-paragraph">A Fallout-inspired Tamagotchi-like game with vault management, character development, and wasteland exploration. Features include resource management, room building, SPECIAL stats, and combat systems.</p>
          <p class="terminal-paragraph">
            <strong>Optimization & Performance:</strong> This game is engineered for smooth, responsive gameplay with a target of 60+ FPS and sub-second initial load times. We utilize asset compression, lazy loading, and prioritized resource management to minimize stalls and memory growth. Real-time FPS and memory monitoring ensure consistent performance, while automated tests verify frame times, dropped frames, and load metrics.
          </p>
          <p class="terminal-paragraph">
            We continuously refine the user experience with modern UI enhancements, responsive design, and seamless animations. Advanced techniques like dynamic resolution scaling and WebAssembly exploration are part of our ongoing efforts to push technical boundaries and deliver an engaging, high-performance experience across devices.
          </p>
          
          <div class="project-stats">
            <div class="project-stat">
              <span class="stat-label">STATUS:</span>
              <span class="stat-value">BETA</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-stat">
              <span class="stat-label">LANGUAGE:</span>
              <span class="stat-value">JAVASCRIPT, SOLIDITY</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-stat">
              <span class="stat-label">LAST COMMIT:</span>
              <span class="stat-value">2025-03-22</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="project-links">
            <a href="https://github.com/NosytLabs/vault-shelter-game" class="terminal-button" target="_blank">VIEW REPOSITORY</a>
